    "items": {
        "title": "Setting the border style",
        "description": "요소의 테두리 스타일을 제어하려면 border-*를 사용하세요.\n",
        "code": "<div class=\"mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg\">\n    <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">테두리 스타일 예제<\/h1>\n    \n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n        <div class=\"border-4 border-solid border-blue-500 p-4 text-center\">\n            solid\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"border-4 border-dashed border-green-500 p-4 text-center\">\n            dashed\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"border-4 border-dotted border-red-500 p-4 text-center\">\n            dotted\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"border-4 border-double border-purple-500 p-4 text-center\">\n            double\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"border-4 border-none p-4 text-center bg-gray-200\">\n            none\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"border-4 border-hidden border-yellow-500 p-4 text-center\">\n            hidden\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-8\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">설명:<\/h2>\n        <ul class=\"list-disc pl-5\">\n            <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded\">border-solid<\/code>: 실선 테두리<\/li>\n            <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded\">border-dashed<\/code>: 파선 테두리<\/li>\n            <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded\">border-dotted<\/code>: 점선 테두리<\/li>\n            <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded\">border-double<\/code>: 이중선 테두리<\/li>\n            <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded\">border-none<\/code>: 테두리 없음<\/li>\n            <li><code class=\"bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded\">border-hidden<\/code>: 테두리 숨김 (none과 유사하지만 표에서 다르게 동작)<\/li>           \n        <\/ul>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>",
        "updated_at": "2024-08-16 06:12:20"
    }
}